project_descr: Areas for Research, Engagement and National Agendas - Creates a more conductive environment for stakeholders including political actors

outputs.output_descr:
The initiation plan (IP) Areas for Research and Engagement on National Agendas (ARENA) creates a more conducive environment for stakeholders to participate in inclusive public policy dialogue about national on big society issues. It improves the capacity of civil society to set agendas to frame public policy in evidence based research, provides a number of different spaces of engagement to develop these policies and it works to anchor these issues in public demand.
Output 1: Increased evidence and research base to set agendas for engagement between actors identifying key governance challenges.

project_title: areas for research, engagement and national agendas
